Text: This is great Dean.  Thanks so much. Will miss Jack D. on the Street.

You are a right little treasure Dean! Thank you ever so much. Your efforts are always appreciated!

Thank you Dean you are a GEM.

this was really good. good to see the old cast members too. and to know why Jack has left.

we did enjoy this and will be keeping this to watch again in the future.
